name: Lacey Lady Gift Tag
description:
Lace always adds a ladylike touch, so why not top off your gift with a yellow lace gift tag? This design is from our new lino block stamp series which are all individually designed and hand carved. This adorable set of 5 tags comes with black and gold bakers twine.

Tags measure 3.75" x 2.75"
5 Tags Total

name: Blue Diamonds Paper Straws
description:
How fun for your next get together! 
These sweet green striped paper straws are adorned with blue diamond wavy flags.

Set of 10 straws w/ pre attached flags

name: Just a Touch of Summer Gold Monogram Set
description:
This summer it's Hip to Be Square with this square monogramed set!

Set has 20 white mounted flat notes and 20 gravel grey envelopes. Each 5"x5" white card is mounted atop a 5.25" x 5.25" plum flat note. Each white card is letterpressed with your single monogram letter of choice in a rich shimmering gold ink. This flat card is finished off with a strip of yellow floral Japanese Washi tape.

In your note to seller at checkout please specify which letter you would like.

name: Doe Looks Like A Lady Card Set
description:
Adorable ladylike doe folded cards! These stamps were hand designed and carved and then used with a moss green shimmer ink (woodgrain) and a chocolate brown shimmer ink (doe). To step up the level of cuteness with this card each bow is accented with antique gold glitter.

This set of 10 cards is accompanied by s antique gold envelope.

Item Breakdown
Card: 4 1/2" x 6 1/4" (folded)
Envelope: 4 3/4" x 6 1/2"
Ink: Shimmer Chocolate, shimmer moss
Amount: 10 card 10 envelope

name: Upcycled Bottle Bud Vases
description:
This set of 3 bud vases is a perfect touch for that bit of upcycled rustic charm. Each vase stands approx. 6.25 inches tall with a base diameter of 2.5 inches. Securely adorned on each vase is a belly band of imported cream with gold brushstroke paper, and a belt of black with gold laced twine.

Important Note: Do to the small neck opening, use a funnel when filling with water to ensure the paper band doesn't become damp.
